{"tid":2107440,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"升市已完結，進入上落市或橫行市","createTime":"2020-07-14T01:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T07:58:11.000Z","uid":76310,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e900d7185ef1a863f171be193fc8681ea5b97362","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:20:06.000Z","msg":"雖然呢一，二個星期大市不斷升<br />\n好多股不斷升<br />\n但去到上星期尾或尋日，大市繼續上，另外只集中升幾隻<br />\n這意味什麼？<br />\n<br />\n一個升市或牛市重臨<br />\n先升指數同強勢股（見底回升，大家還在恐慌中）<br />\n然後擴散至大部份股（大市開始核爆，大戶開始入市）<br />\n之後稍稍收窄至某類別股（大市繼續上，散戶開始入市）<br />\n之後只升幾隻（升市尾段，連師奶學生都入市，但唔夠錢，只能谷大市和幾隻主力股）<br />\n<br />\n大市玩完需調整，之後進入上落格局或橫行市況"},{"pid":"810376d29ca4bf816b99052e2f7c7155d5aa934e","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:23:03.000Z","msg":"尋日都只係升中芯同騰訊<br />\n上星期尾就主力炒美團，中芯和騰訊<br />\n但其實好多股唔郁<br />\n<br />\n集中炒幾隻<br />\n<br />\n而昨晚老美單日轉向，代表個市玩完"},{"pid":"950ebc88674ece2ac050268e4bb7ae7eadf65115","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"大市已完 等下輪"},{"pid":"e12de1abc8ac4b313e14f8d70d293ec4c50c72ef","tid":2107440,"uid":168381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"連燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9387938f97fac941dcb45256b4a36e55a81dc542","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"其實新聞一話好易搵錢<br />\n好多股神出現時已經有戒心<br />\n但大市繼續上和主力升幾隻<br />\n就由佢<br />\n<br />\n但老美單日大轉向<br />\n覺得已經出事玩完"},{"pid":"dd45ff4bae9bb83f1d8c187c9dafad15e7fda75e","tid":2107440,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9387938f97fac941dcb45256b4a36e55a81dc542","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"其實新聞一話好易搵錢<br />\n好多股神出現時已經有戒心<br />\n但大市繼續上和主力升幾隻<br />\n就由佢<br />\n<br />\n但老美單日大轉向<br />\n覺得已經出事玩完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:56:37.000Z","msg":"覺得美團同阿里將來升定跌?<br />\n諗緊好冇趁佢跌入手"},{"pid":"7754f66bb7ad4f92a02591e5fd47eb672ab19f31","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"不過唔會一下子落<br />\n係高位反覆，落上落上一陣先落<br />\n<br />\n原因係仲有最後既資金入市接火捧可以頂一頂個市，另外原因係大戶炒左上黎都要時間散貨"},{"pid":"14bd75fb9aeb2c34e2511ff267aaf328035f18c0","tid":2107440,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"未俾人夾死？"},{"pid":"5d77844dbed7476a6d37b3c2c7d264daef411b4e","tid":2107440,"uid":97314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"早幾日開post話40000點，今日又話升市完<br />\n<br />\n樓主精神分裂？"},{"pid":"fdd956af2608abf77559cc6732a9e974f4dfe873","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"落得比想像中快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d22c7a459dd9354dccc2d583d0f49887fa569b","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d77844dbed7476a6d37b3c2c7d264daef411b4e","tid":2107440,"uid":97314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"早幾日開post話40000點，今日又話升市完<br />\n<br />\n樓主精神分裂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"睇市場訊號<br />\n前幾日仲好<br />\n梗係吹到天下無敵"},{"pid":"72f36982522c9befc36210adfced96ef43eef457","tid":2107440,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"樂觀的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15698ffa4441db20ffb7807396216f4da48c4566","tid":2107440,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T02:55:14.000Z","msg":"學生師奶入市 股神出現<br />\n大市要調整 係正路既"},{"pid":"e73588f9ecc56c82add672b02138612986186d74","tid":2107440,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"樓主講到咁堅 肯定係股壇再世孔明<i